class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T20:04:47.000Z","msg":"點解咁講？"},{"pid":"e89c8b6f2423c377a937081564a35379b06fda61","tid":533011,"uid":121131,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T20:23:37.000Z","msg":"近幾年開嘅公司電話好多係3字頭"},{"pid":"d8d08db1958c0915e7376268ef24efba8e9d1384","tid":533011,"uid":41619,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T20:38:43.000Z","msg":"[真人真事]<br />\n有次我閒日放假<br />\n瞓到上晝十一點幾<br />\n畀個cold call嘈撚醒咗<br />\n我屌撚到佢化<br />\n之後成個禮拜屋企都有條fax line打黎<br />\n你一聽就會聽到啲好似你打去啲fax line聽到o既noise<br />\n自此 我都冇再屌啲仆街cold call<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯有見到phone book冇o既唔聽<br />\n之後上網check個電話<br />\n如果佢係緊要的話 對方就好自然會打多幾次<br />\n但係都係果句<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Cold call 狗不得好死<br />\n全家世世代代畀狗屌</span></span></strong><br />\n咪撚同我講咩撚野「人地都係打份工啫」「人地都有老母生」「人地都有情緒」<br />\n都係果句<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Cold call 狗食撚屎啦 屌你老母</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"fbfe37b5be7f2145f79131e3deafa8db4b9e624e","tid":533011,"uid":74751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T22:06:08.000Z","msg":"正傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2318dc6c269bfb8e4b487344849f62f92fb5a98a","tid":533011,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T22:12:26.000Z","msg":"醫院電話都會3字頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f8ed5725b75bd93ab47b325d33ce7c9965ad18","tid":533011,"uid":26764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2318dc6c269bfb8e4b487344849f62f92fb5a98a","tid":533011,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T22:12:26.000Z","msg":"醫院電話都會3字頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201