個行業真係要死全家ge, 無撚端端喺度煩鳩住曬人哋. <br />\n其實政府應該一早已經開始取締呢啲白痴行業啦....擾民到呢...."},{"pid":"d3764ffd2dc1cf2dbf511c55c95599ef23790132","tid":533011,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T00:31:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己on9唔搞清楚就賴人<br />\n大把屋企電話，公司電話都係3字頭啦</blockquote><br />\n但係其實佢講嘢都唔係冇道理喎, 例如有啲醫院轉咗電話係三字頭. <br />\nd病人見到有三字頭嘅電話都唔知接唔接好, 都試過有人係因為咁樣miss咗電話, 報紙都上過啦."},{"pid":"1335fb04d106f3bd6820e18ab512fd8b41af707b","tid":533011,"uid":10044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T00:43:10.000Z","msg":"試過屌佢老母 夠膽打返比我互屌"},{"pid":"8c6d8269ac90925a094feb4c97a5151072afa36d","tid":533011,"uid":66945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T00:46:13.000Z","msg":"搵工嗰輪真係乜電話都聽<br />\n平時唔知咩電話直接cut線"},{"pid":"f1c80848821a1732b80cd8f5f5c13f5892acfb32","tid":533011,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T00:55:17.000Z","msg":"點解唔用小熊來電呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"352a9e5b7c5f028ac9be98dfb00923e77d78aa51","tid":533011,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46d5bc6e8c16c19b26c5d0b32c9f19407393580d","tid":533011,"uid":93855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T11:26:08.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母<br />\n頭先有個3字頭電話打黎<br />\n我以為cold call狗 一聽就屌鳩佢老母就cut線<br />\n然後佢仲繼續call我2次<br />\n我咪check個電話咩料<br />\n仆街啦 原來人事部打黎叫我返工<br />\n我屌你老母點撚算好啊<br />\ncold call狗我屌你老母！！！！！！！！！！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T01:36:01.000Z","msg":"你依啲咪正宗戇鳩仔囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔聽清楚咩事就亂鳩咁屌"},{"pid":"e90f29b88ae9022e0fd07e8a9f559abfc8ab5261","tid":533011,"uid":93855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7082a47325b08146ae3b0b0e984c96503a2dac8","tid":533011,"uid":39016,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T17:39:09.000Z","msg":"抵撚死啦 樓主鑊鑊都咁蠢 間公司好彩<img src=\"/ass